## Feature Tracking

Track features in `.claude/context/features/`:

```bash
# Create a new feature file
touch .claude/context/features/$(date +%Y%m%d)-my-feature.md
```

Feature files track:
- Status (PLANNING, IN_PROGRESS, TESTING, IN_REVIEW, COMPLETE)
- Requirements checklist
- Technical approach
- Task assignments

